  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Post is one of the best known hotels in St. Anton and has been a special Inghams partner for many years. The traditional hotel has been extensively modernised over the years and is popular for its excellent service and prime location.</p>
<h2>Central village location</h2>
<p>You will be situated in an unbeatable location right in the heart of <a data-udi="umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855}" title="St Anton">St. Anton</a> on the main high street. Just 100 metres away is the main Galzig lift and slopes so you can easily explore the whole <a data-udi="umb://document/c24998bb7c5140ed8ec0febaf0a46fa2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c24998bb7c5140ed8ec0febaf0a46fa2}" title="Arlberg Ski Area">Arlberg Ski Area.</a></p>
<h2>Family-run hotel</h2>
<p>The friendly Alber family are rightfully proud of their reputation for good food and personal service. Their comfortable hotel has a relaxed atmosphere and is spacious and elegant throughout. </p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Post the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
