  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>St Anton Rooms </strong>are around 20-24m² and have either bath or shower. They are traditionally furnished with an Austrian twin bed, they sleep up to two adults.</p>
<p><strong>Galzig</strong> <strong>Rooms </strong>are around 26-33m² and are more spacious. These rooms have a seating area and also have a bath. An additional double sofa bed mean these rooms can sleep up to three.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms </strong>are around 14-20m². These rooms can have a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Minifridge</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Bathrobes</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
